        { q: "Is Fryeburg opted in to recreational cannabis?", a: "Yes. Fryeburg has authorized recreational cannabis dispensaries and is notable for having the first recreational dispensary in western Maine." },
        { q: "Why is Fryeburg significant for cannabis retail?", a: "Fryeburg's location on the New Hampshire border captures cross-state traffic from NH residents. Additionally, the Fryeburg Fair draws 200,000+ visitors annually, creating a massive seasonal surge." },
        { q: "What makes The Glass Cook unique?", a: "The Glass Cook combines a recreational cannabis dispensary with an on-site glassblowing studio, offering a unique experiential retail environment." }
      ]}
    />
  </section>

  <p class="disclaimer"><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Information is provided for general reference only. Dispensary status, hours, and product availability can change. Always verify details directly with the dispensary before planning a visit.</p>
